OL,3,CThe Ukrainian families who fell in
OL,4,Clove with Wales after escaping war
OL,6,FLana said: "I want to save my son from
OL,7,Fwar so I'm here. It's a hard decision
OL,8,Ffor us to come here as we don't know
OL,9,Fthis country and we don't know any
OL,10,Fperson here and we left our life in
OL,11,FUkraine, our home, job, friends."
OL,13,FAlthough Lana and her husband Oleg
OL,14,Ffound love in Wales but their heart is
OL,15,Fback in Ukraine.
OL,17,FSvitlana Kovalova said: "It's our love
OL,18,Fstory and I think it's a miracle
OL,19,Fbecause we were here in Cardiff when
OL,20,Fwe met and not in Ukraine."
