OL,6,FHer husband Oleg Kocherzhenko added:
OL,7,F"My life was difficult and it is still
OL,8,Fdifficult because my work is in
OL,9,FUkraine and a lot of staff members go
OL,10,Fthere but at the same time I'm happy
OL,11,Fhere."
OL,13,FMatvii, Lana's son has found a new
OL,14,Flife here, new school and friends.
