OL,3,CThe Ukrainian families who fell in
OL,4,Clove with Wales after escaping war
OL,6,FMatvii said: "I feel very nice because
OL,7,FI have a very nice school. It's near
OL,8,Fmy house and it only take me around 15
OL,9,Fminutes to reach there. I have friends
OL,10,Fin my class and other classes. I would
OL,11,Flike to be a programmer because I
OL,12,Fthink it's a really nice job.
OL,14,F"I would like to travel around the
OL,15,Fworld when I grow up and just work
OL,16,Fonline."
OL,18,FITV Wales spoke to Lana and her family
OL,19,Flast year when they were living with
OL,20,FCaroline and her husband Alex.
