OL,3,CThe Ukrainian families who fell in
OL,4,Clove with Wales after escaping war
OL,6,FIt was their first experience of Welsh
OL,7,Flife.
OL,9,FTwo years ago, Ukrainians were living
OL,10,Fa normal life back home but the war
OL,11,Freshaped the lives of millions.
OL,13,FSome of them came to Wales and have
OL,14,Fbeen trying to build a life here. Now
OL,15,Fafter two years later, the return home
OL,16,Ffor these families seem unlikely to
OL,17,Fhappen.
OL,19,FIn Swansea, for Natalia's family, it
OL,20,Fhasn't been plain sailing.
