OL,3,CThe Ukrainian families who fell in
OL,4,Clove with Wales after escaping war
OL,6,FThey lived in a hotel room for nine
OL,7,Fmonths, they were faced with the
OL,8,Fprospect of moving to a holiday park
OL,9,Fin north Wales.
OL,11,FITV Wales' report last year helped to
OL,12,Fkeep them in Swansea and we followed
OL,13,Ftheir journey to the first place they
OL,14,Fcalled home.
OL,16,FBut they've never lost connection with
OL,17,FUkraine.
