OL,3,CThe Ukrainian families who fell in
OL,4,Clove with Wales after escaping war
OL,6,FNatalia said: "Now we've found our new
OL,7,Fhome and situation in Ukraine is
OL,8,Fgetting worse from last year. But life
OL,9,Fgoes on and we must live. Now we have
OL,10,Four roots in Wales."
OL,12,FFor Natalia's family their love for
OL,13,Fmusic kept them going.
OL,15,FHer older daughter, Mary Mikulska
OL,16,Fsaid: "I'm really happy that I can
OL,17,Fstill learn music here and I enjoy it.
OL,18,FIn Ukraine I had finished my music
OL,19,Fschool."
