OL,3,CThe Ukrainian families who fell in
OL,4,Clove with Wales after escaping war
OL,6,FHer younger daughter added: " I feel
OL,7,Fokay in Wales but I really miss my
OL,8,Fbrothers too and I want to go back to
OL,9,FUkraine but people in Wales are so
OL,10,Fnice and kind."
OL,12,FTheir message is to remind the world
OL,13,Fof the war in Ukraine with a heart
OL,14,Ffull of love for a land they left
OL,15,Fbehind.
OL,17,FNatalia added: " This is the key of
OL,18,Four own house and I'm very grateful. I
OL,19,Fwant to build my future life in Wales.
OL,20,FI know that we have a war in our land."
